import { createApp } from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import router from './router'
import Vue from 'vue'
import formCreate from '@form-create/element-ui'
import FcDesigner from '@form-create/designer'

Vue.use(formCreate)
Vue.use(FcDesigner)

createApp(App).use(router).mount('#app')
